@page "/"

<PageTitle>Car Price Predictor</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to Car Price Predictor</h1>

<p>
    This application uses Machine Learning to help you determine if a car's price is fair.
    Simply enter the car details and the asking price, and we'll tell you if it's:
</p>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Too High</strong> - The asking price is above market value</li>
    <li><strong>Good Price</strong> - The asking price is within fair market range</li>
    <li><strong>Too Low</strong> - The asking price is below market value</li>
</ul>

<p>
    <a href="/predict" class="btn btn-primary">Start Price Check</a>
</p>

<h3>How it works</h3>
<ol>
    <li>Enter the car's make, model, year, mileage, fuel type, and other details</li>
    <li>Enter the asking price you're considering</li>
    <li>Our ML model analyzes the data against thousands of car listings</li>
    <li>Get instant feedback on the price and see the typical price range</li>
</ol>
